@NODE Introduction
@{B}Introduction@{UB}

With ExtractLGP, you will be able to extract files from LGP archives
used by PC version of Final Fantasy VII.  It will not work with
PlayStation version.  As far as I know, only FF7 used LGP archives.  I
only used this program to listen to the original MIDI files from FF7.

@ENDNODE

