@NODE Requirements
@{B}Requirements@{UB}

- AmigaOS 2.04 or better.

@ENDNODE

@NODE Installation
@{B}How To Install@{UB}

There is no installation script provided yet.  Just copy the main
executable to anywhere you like but preferrably in command path.

@ENDNODE

@NODE Usage
@{B}How To Use@{UB}

You can only use this program from CLI.


@{U}Template@{UU}

ExtractLGP FILE/A

FILE/A  : name of the LGP archive to extract files from.


All the files will be extracted to the CLI's current directory.

@ENDNODE

